Text:
I think there is something wrong with this torrent !

I have 100 percent of "the girl who kicked..." i I can't play them, when I right click the files the only option I get is OPEN and SEND TO.

When I look on the preferences of the files it says that they are 0 kb instead of 2 gb.

Can anyone confirm this ? - Or is it just me...

But thanks for a great upload!

I found the problem !

The files name were to long, the name together with the directory name gave a to long search path, I copied the "the girl who kicked..." - directory to another disk and it works just fine.

Thanks again
